            "title": "Description of Echolocation Call Parameters for Urban Bats in Vietnam as a Step Towards a More Integrated Acoustic Monitoring of Urban Wildlife in Southeast Asia",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Long Kim",
                    "lastName": "Pham"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
